project_descr: The project will support the capitalization of biodiversity Trust Fund Bioguine Foundation and IBAP to effectively manage the National Protected Area System, particularly the management of the Castanhez National Park.

outputs.output_descr: A sustainable financial mechanism will be in place supporting the National Protected Area System and IBAP's capacity to effectively manage the Cantanhez National Park will be reinforced through a comprehensive capacity development program implementation.
